name: betterMix_Anime
description:
-Update 4/29/2023

betterMix3.0_Anime and betterMix3.0(with_cetus)_Anime is added.

3.0 is a general improvement on 2.0, focusing on better eyes, anatomy (and a bit better hands) while maintaining most of the features of 2.0 like wonderful color and light and shadow.

3.0 (with cetus) mixed cetusMix inside. Compared to 3.0, it sacrifices some color and light effect in exchange for better anatomy.

This model is SUPER COMPATIBLE with other "small" models like LoRAs (LyCoRis, LoHA, LoCon) and embeddings. I highly recommend using this model as a base for other models' mixture.

All the example images provided here are using hiten1 and EasyNegative these 2 embeddings.

The link to hiten1 embedding:

https://civitai.com/models/15430/hiten-style

The link to EasyNegative embedding:

https://civitai.com/models/7808/easynegative

-

This model is made by merging PastelMix, Anything3.0 and OrangeMix together.

I mainly use this model to cooperate with the "hiten1" embedding (textual inversion) I made, the link to it is above.

Suggested basic parameters:

  • Sampler: Euler a & DPM++ 2M Karras

  • Sampling steps: 20

  • CFG scale: 7

Recommend to use this model with highres fix on.

Suggested highres fix parameters:

  • Upscaler: Latent

  • highres steps: 20

  • Denoising: 0.6

  • Upscale from 640 360 to 1280 720

I've also uploaded this model to hugging face, link is below

https://huggingface.co/SakanakoChan/BetterMix2.0_Anime

如果可以关注我的bilibili频道的话我会很感谢的！

I'd be grateful if you can follow my bilibili channel!

https://space.bilibili.com/11779368
